{"type": "article", "id": 13055, "title": "“自然”首饰系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-05T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000235n7syxVMrwRpdOX4K.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t波兰设计师 Agata Bieleń 和 Mosses Lichen 联手推出了一个“自然”首饰系列，其灵感来源皆是大自然，莲花，水中的动物等等，这些作品线条非常柔美，设计师试图既能够保存自然的灵动，又能让首饰恰如其分地修饰女性的温婉和柔美气质，整个系列看起来都仙气十足。<a href=\"http://agatabielen.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看 Agata Bieleń 更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140718Zzj5HysLDnKu9fht.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140718a7G5zgJx9MLZe3EU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140718E29L73CKVOnIgrpj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140719kWg3Ebl1iJUhCvLd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261407192in0KWNH3DsOuvTo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140719MEYH6QtsGyBLS3Jv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140720asxH1DqWXB9cGj20.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}